name: Online Mentoring
description: Let’s have a conversation about your career to discuss your hopes for the future and the challenges that are holding you back. We’ll review the current challenges that are holding you back and determine the best strategy to get you moving forward in your career.

name: ONE-TO-ONE Coaching
description: During this coaching program, you’ll navigate through a soul-searching journey that will explore your past career choices, hidden strengths, personality traits, passions and interests. Through this process, you’ll discover how to nurture your career and find momentum to propel you down the right career path.

name: Job Search Mentoring
description: Find a job that fits your personality through support with your resume, cover letters, job search, networking, and salary negotiation. Get customized feedback on your resume and cover letter format and content. This includes personalized resume and cover letter support outside of our 4 coaching sessions.

name: IN-DEPTH Thinking
description: So now you have a great new resume! Do you know how to get it in the hands of someone who can hire you? I can work with you to develop a smart, proactive strategy to maximize your opportunities. (Hint: it involves more than looking at online job sites.

name: Business Planning
description: I focus on providing actionable and advanced market search strategies that convert into offers. Whether you need help finding the right investment, networking with key decision-makers, or interviewing like a pro, I got your back.

name: Resume Monitoring
description: Resumes, cover letters, and LinkedIn profiles should not be one-size-fits-all documents. A normal template you found online or a resume won’t make you stand out and get offered interviews. Each piece should be tailored to fit your career goal.
